    "an6.143-169:0.2": "13. Abbreviated Texts Beginning with Greed ",
    "an6.143-169:0.3": "Untitled Discourses on Greed, Etc. ",
    "an6.143-169:1.1": "“For the complete understanding of greed … ",
    "an6.143-169:1.2": "complete ending … ",
